    {
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Welcome to Decipad! 2.0"
        }
      ],
      "type": "title",
      "id": "Fu-Tub2k7PGZC9M7na7nI"
    },
    {
      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Hi and "
            },
            {
              "text": "welcome to Decipad",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": "! \n\nDecipad is a productivity tool for growth stage founders and teams.\n\nDecipad will transform how you do reporting and planning without the need for a dedicated data team."
            }
          ],
          "type": "p",
          "id": "SejRXXdfD9ycqebmUewwE"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Decipad is the perfect tool for your team to run your weekly reports: WBRs, sales reviews, etc."
                }
              ],
              "type": "blockquote",
              "id": "9aixiDOr4x8jsjPd5CAgm"
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Data is everywhere, and so having a data team or data skills is super important. Decipad is designed to lower the barrier to working with data. It allows more people to report and work with data without the need to know how to code. "
                }
              ],
              "id": "7OzKUEoUb3KMqncti4s-t",
              "type": "p"
            }
          ],
          "id": "nb4_iA15o1EGWvCZwXT1-",
          "type": "columns"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The basics"
            }
          ],
          "type": "h2",
          "id": "gBbflXueKcsURlmwDm1Ll"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "id": "JVrLOZa_CTHq5AViqG4FP",
          "type": "divider"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Working with your own data"
            }
          ],
          "type": "h3",
          "id": "LUtStcjgR8xb8Qd0NMGKO"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "id": "Kx6EmJeVa_krKnpYL8vy4",
          "type": "divider"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "First thing you want to do with Decipad is getting your data in. That's what our integration block allows you do to:"
            }
          ],
          "type": "p",
          "id": "sF5p662JVtQIqOCV1We1B"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Type "
            },
            {
              "text": "/",
              "code": true,
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": " to open the menu and type "
            },
            {
              "text": "/integration",
              "code": true,
              "bold": true
            }
          ],
          "id": "5T0LFlB609OvH02-GPQlM",
          "type": "p"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "We have easy ways to connect to your data, for instance from "
            },
            {
              "text": "Notion",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "text": "Google Sheets",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": " or simply upload a "
            },
            {
              "text": "CSV",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": ". If you find that you need to connect to  a service that is not listed, you can use a "
            },
            {
              "text": "Code integration",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": " for using any API, or "
            },
            {
              "text": "SQL",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": " to access a database.\n"
            }
          ],
          "type": "p",
          "id": "ZNvvW360JVFLh9SlAesMq"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ],
          "id": "R870_Nt3VYLou-qNWkRif",
          "type": "p"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Above is a CSV added to Decipad containing a conversion funnel. You can refresh the data by clicking the refresh button â€” this won't do anything for a CSV for in a live connection to a service, sheet, or notion it would update your data."
