        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Decipad was built so you can share your documents with confidence. There's basically two types of users for Decipad: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Readers",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "text": "Editors",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": ".  When you are building a document you are in editor mode, but when you "
            },
            {
              "text": "Share",
              "code": true,
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": " with a reader they can only change numbers you put on "
            },
            {
              "text": "widgets",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": " or "
