          "type": "divider"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Collaboration is built into Decipad. When you are adding team-mates you can add them to your workspace. They then become editors on all documents for that workspace. "
            }
          ],
          "type": "p",
          "id": "8wi7zd42NfavOuJFTVlJp"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "When you "
            },
            {
              "text": "Publish",
              "code": true,
              "bold": true
            },
            {
              "text": " documents (for instance to "
            },
            {
              "text": "share with a client",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": ", or to "
            },
            {
              "text": "embed in your website",
              "highlight": true
            },
            {
              "text": ") people can interact with your documents without ever breaking what you built."
            }
          ],
          "type": "p",
          "id": "8WIiJu8YgSxI3O4xje63Y"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "By default all documents in Decipad can be duplicated. If you want to prevent clients or prospects from reading your hidden tabs and blocks, you need to publish by Private URL and not allow readers to duplicate."
            }
          ],
          "type": "callout",
          "id": "wdazjl8IOaN4osT6sdImv",
          "color": "Sun",
          "icon": "AnnotationWarning"
        },
